about.summary: Wkhtmltopdf python wrapper to convert html to pdf

name: python-pdfkit
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set pypi_name = "pdfkit" %}
{% set name = "python-pdfkit" %}
{% set version = "0.6.1" %}
{% set sha256 = "ef1da35b78d534197e7ce4a604a4a190e9aa769e56634957535f3479a50d8cd1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ pypi_name[0] }}/{{ pypi_name}}/{{ pypi_name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt
  # wkhtmltopdf is not yet available on Windows or Mac
  skip: True  # [win or osx]

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - wkhtmltopdf

test:
  imports:
    - pdfkit

about:
  home: https://github.com/JazzCore/python-pdfkit
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Wkhtmltopdf python wrapper to convert html to pdf'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - scopatz
